    <dialogue-node nodeindex="0" editor-x="0" editor-y="0">
      <speak-char idTarget="Balta">
        <resources name="No name" />
        <text>Hey Pablo, what's that noise?</text>
      </speak-char>
      <condition />
      <speak-player>
        <resources name="No name" />
        <text>There's a fire in the buliding, we must evacuate all staff immediately</text>
      </speak-player>
      <condition />
      <speak-char idTarget="Balta">
        <resources name="No name" />
        <text>And where is the fire?</text>
      </speak-char>
      <condition />
      <child nodeindex="1" />
    </dialogue-node>
    <option-node nodeindex="1" preListening="yes" editor-x="0" editor-y="0" x="0" y="0">
      <speak-player>
        <text>That doesn't matter at all!</text>
        <resources name="No name" />
      </speak-player>
      <condition />
      <child nodeindex="2" />
      <speak-player>
        <text>In office 411</text>
        <resources name="No name" />
      </speak-player>
      <condition />
      <child nodeindex="3" />
      <speak-player>
        <text>In office 411, it's a huge fire. Every man for himself!</text>
        <resources name="No name" />
      </speak-player>
      <condition />
      <child nodeindex="4" />
    </option-node>
    <dialogue-node nodeindex="2" editor-x="0" editor-y="0">
      <speak-char idTarget="Balta">
        <resources name="No name" />
        <text>You're not helping me, I can't know where to go</text>
      </speak-char>
      <condition />
      <child nodeindex="1" />
    </dialogue-node>
    <dialogue-node nodeindex="3" editor-x="0" editor-y="0">
      <speak-char idTarget="Balta">
        <resources name="No name" />
        <text>Wow, it's everyone OK?</text>
      </speak-char>
      <condition />
      <child nodeindex="5" />
    </dialogue-node>
    <dialogue-node nodeindex="4" editor-x="0" editor-y="0">
      <speak-char idTarget="Balta">
        <resources name="No name" />
        <text>Help! Run!</text>
      </speak-char>
      <condition />
      <end-conversation>
        <effect>
          <activate flag="PanicSituationFlag" guid="ef28d839-acd5-4859-a28c-bbb9abfd4039" />
          <condition />
          <activate flag="GameOver" guid="4f7e7704-75d4-48c6-9374-fc4171c96ac5" />
          <condition />
        </effect>
      </end-conversation>
    </dialogue-node>
    <option-node nodeindex="5" preListening="yes" editor-x="0" editor-y="0" x="0" y="0">
      <speak-player>
        <text>The office was empty. I guess everyone fled when the fire started.</text>
        <resources name="No name" />
      </speak-player>
      <condition />
      <child nodeindex="6" />
      <speak-player>
        <text>I think we lost all the helpers, every man for himself!</text>
        <resources name="No name" />
      </speak-player>
      <condition />
      <child nodeindex="7" />
    </option-node>
    <dialogue-node nodeindex="6" editor-x="0" editor-y="0">
      <speak-char idTarget="Balta">
        <resources name="No name" />
        <text>Ok, fine, let me finish this backups and I'll be downstairs in a minute...</text>
      </speak-char>
      <condition />
      <child nodeindex="8" />
    </dialogue-node>
    <dialogue-node nodeindex="7" editor-x="0" editor-y="0">
      <end-conversation>
        <effect>
          <activate flag="GameOver" guid="8b395728-9bcb-4bff-82fc-727906d9895c" />
          <condition />
          <activate flag="PanicSituationFlag" guid="4ac790fd-0649-4225-b6d7-fb7e865d2791" />
          <condition />
        </effect>
      </end-conversation>
    </dialogue-node>
    <option-node nodeindex="8" preListening="yes" editor-x="0" editor-y="0" x="0" y="0">
      <speak-player>
        <text>No way! It's a serious fire, we must keep calm but evacuate fast.</text>
        <resources name="No name" />
      </speak-player>
      <condition />
      <child nodeindex="9" />
      <speak-player>
        <text>Don't be silly, we have to evacuate the building NOW!</text>
        <resources name="No name" />
      </speak-player>
      <condition />
      <child nodeindex="10" />
    </option-node>
    <dialogue-node nodeindex="9" editor-x="0" editor-y="0">
      <child nodeindex="11" />
    </dialogue-node>
    <dialogue-node nodeindex="10" editor-x="0" editor-y="0">
      <child nodeindex="11" />
    </dialogue-node>
    <dialogue-node nodeindex="11" editor-x="0" editor-y="0">
      <speak-char idTarget="Balta">
        <resources name="No name" />
        <text>Ok, fine, take it easy, I didn't think  it was so urgent...</text>
      </speak-char>
      <condition />
      <speak-player>
        <resources name="No name" />
        <text>Well, it is, we have to move fast, but calmly.</text>
      </speak-player>
      <condition />
      <speak-char idTarget="Balta">
        <resources name="No name" />
        <text>OK, let me get my things and we go</text>
      </speak-char>
      <condition />
      <child nodeindex="12" />
    </dialogue-node>
    <option-node nodeindex="12" preListening="yes" editor-x="0" editor-y="0" x="0" y="0">
      <speak-player>
        <text>Ok, but hurry up</text>
        <resources name="No name" />
      </speak-player>
      <condition />
      <child nodeindex="13" />
      <speak-player>
        <text>I said no, you can't check anything. We leave now.</text>
